        <abstract>
            <p>Encourages JS to continue work on coloured primrose. No one has noticed this since Gärtner. CD will send his own data for JS’s use and will read MS when ready. Advises JS to repeat experiments if evidence is weak – for his reputation’s sake and for satisfaction at fully establishing a fact.</p> 
<p>Treviranus made a slip of pen in writing of <hi rend="italic">Primula longiflora</hi> as short-styled.</p> 
        </abstract>
